{
  "stem": "10818.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, made them into servants or whatever and, and sometimes treated them extremely well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was-- I had been assigned to a school, which, of which some of the alumni had organized, through a wonderful woman called May Pickard, who was one of the alumni of the school called Culcheth Hall in Bowdon, Cheshire, who decided to take in five German Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't have to be totally Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They could be part Jewish because as far as Hitler was concerned, they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a girls' school which had run a little low on boarders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a boarding school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I guess the people who made up that committee of, of alumni sponsored these girls and in a way helped their school out also at the same time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and when we got there, we were picked up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were three of us from Mainz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were two other girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the three of us travelled together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one of them was only about 11.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she was terribly homesick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She didn't speak a word of English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she never saw her parents again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She did see her grandmother again, who was not Jewish, after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She's now living in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I'm still in touch with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, we, we were gathered up and taken to near Manchester, where this school was, in, in north of England.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they had uniforms, school uniforms waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In England, the schools wore uniforms, the school girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were-- immediately, they tried to integrate us in the school as best they could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It, it worked, in my case, certainly.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
